Codes : 

GenXmlSign.java for signing metadata files
Usage: java GenXmlSign [medatadalfile] [outputfile] [P12 GridCertificate] [P12 GridCertificate Passwd]

ValidateSign.java to verify and validate metadata file. 
Usage : java ValidateSign signedmetadatafile centos.xml : metadatfile for testing

Example : 

To sign : 
java GenXmlSign centos_dc.xml centos_dc_output.xml  myGridCert.p12 relatedpasswd



To verify and validate : 

java ValidateSign centos_dc_output.xml


